name: Dynamic Active Emerging Markets ETF
longDescription: DXEM seeks to provide long-term capital appreciation by investing primarily in equity securities of companies that are located or doing business in emerging or developing market countries. In seeking to achieve its investment objectives, DXEM invests primarily in equity securities of companies operating in emerging or developing market countries. The Manager generally follows a focused and long-term oriented investment approach to meet required objectives.
